org.nerd4j.csv.field.converter

Class StringToDate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.nerd4j.csv.field.converter.AbstractCSVFieldConverter<String,Date>
      • org.nerd4j.csv.field.converter.StringToDate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CSVProcessOperation, CSVFieldConverter<String,Date>, CSVRegistryEntry

    public final class StringToDate
extends AbstractCSVFieldConverter<String,Date>
    Implementation of the CSVFieldConverter interface that converts Strings into Dates.

    This converter uses a DateFormat to perform the conversion. Therefore it requires the pattern to use during the parsing. All the informations on how to write the date pattern can be found in the javaDoc of the DateFormat class.

    Author:
    Nerd4j Team
